            <title>[FLINK-36242] Fix unstable test in MaterializedTableITCase</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-36242</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;Errormessage%3A&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Error message:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
